data.description: The best location in the entire neighborhood. Hurry over and check this out! 4 bedroom plus bonus room in great community near everything! Step out your front door and enjoy the heated community pool and spa (it's like having your own without any upkeep or expense). Brand new carpet and paint throughout. Huge gourmet granite island kitchen with gorgeous highly upgraded cabinets all open to spacious family room. Large master suite with separate tub/shower, his/hers closets too! The bonus room has a gas fp, great ambiance for the cool winter days ahead. A great opportunity, short distance to huge play area too! So, if you are looking for an amazing home,  zero maintenance, with a spectacular kitchen, immediate access to pool/spa/play area with nothing but unpacking to do-here it is!
